{"type": "article", "id": 60222, "title": "今年欧洲最值得一住的度假小屋，你想去哪个？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计", "date": "2019-01-12T22:45:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 272, "name": "建筑设计"}, {"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 9528, "name": "酒店设计"}, {"id": 55876, "name": "度假小屋"}, {"id": 55877, "name": "Dualchas Architects"}, {"id": 55878, "name": "TYIN Tegnestue Architects"}, {"id": 55879, "name": "Rental Eggertsson Architects"}, {"id": 55880, "name": "Andreas Sell"}, {"id": 55881, "name": "Walter Angonese"}, {"id": 55882, "name": "Manfred Alois Mayr"}, {"id": 55883, "name": "Pedro Domingos"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 354, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190112070441uZWdQX0EjiIlz3N6.jpg", "contents": "<p oncecleanhtml=\"true\">德国有家网站，叫做 <a href=\"https://www.urlaubsarchitektur.de\" rel=\"nofollow\">Urlaubs Architektur</a>，创始人都是建筑师。他们的目的，就是想要建立一个“反 Airbnb”的真正民宿平台，精选了世界各地的优质体验感、设计感民宿。最近，它们出版了新书《假日建筑》（<a href=\"https://www.urlaubsarchitektur.de/de/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Holiday Architecture</em></a>），里面选出了一批今年可以租到的欧洲度假小屋。</p><p>这个周末，我们一起来看看其中的一些亮点，是否可能成为你今年旅行计划中的一站。</p><h3>Hermitage Sykaminea by Andreas Sell</h3><p>想要逃脱都市喧嚣，这家位于希腊 Lesbos 最高山脉上的 Hermitage Sykaminea 酒店是个不错的选择。它掩映在橄榄树林中，坐享土耳其海岸一览无余的美景。</p><p>整个酒店的主体，是一个隐蔽的木质屋子，以及藏在后方的石头浴室，住宅建筑适应梯田地形，因此内部延伸三层。</p><p>室内设计简约克制，陈设也很简单，以模仿当地农民曾经在收获期间用作住宿的简陋棚屋的美感。它只提供简单的日常生活需求，在房子里没有自来水，必须带入淡水，所有的运行都来自于太阳能，客人可以在这完全远离网络，回归自然原始的生活。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070827mNk1QTGvM67noBXc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.794000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070734XNaBETyc48lzAr9H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.714000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070736IlOguKYDvGWBzfre.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.710000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070542opTi1H9BU7SgVdjF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070543UN5pgxjSuRGJithv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501377\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901120705430WSO56AhLepDlZFQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.994505\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070544BaPn8dxT7uD56fNW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.998168\" data-format=\"png\"><figcaption>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.urlaubsarchitektur.de\" rel=\"nofollow\">Urlaubs Architektur</a></figcaption> </figure></div><h3>Casa Agostos by Pedro Domingos</h3><p>巨大的长方形开口点缀在葡萄牙阿尔加维地区南部这栋住宅的苍白外观上，可欣赏到周围自然保护区的景色，周围环绕着粗野生长的橄榄树和开花灌木。</p><p>整个有两个相似大小的庭院，一个朝向厨房，另一个朝向起居室，大窗户、天窗与庭院灯光相结合。建筑师 Pedro Domingos 对这幢老宅进行了大修和扩建，以创造一系列平静的白色生活空间和天窗，使内部充满自然光。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070904h62eg3KDyEtXUCTb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665098\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070904cnzCQ7lGojuS0KTv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070905vCkRehKMXcLtzonE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665098\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070905PUGy2pSs7I6YCWrc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070906atdrSwcUoxWXeA1h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070906YP6tDauowTVr3dMe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665098\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112070907UrF9ChzBOdvW2ZLD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.archdaily.com/236587/house-of-agostos-pedro-domingos-arquitectos/5018226f28ba0d48240006c5-house-of-agostos-pedro-domingos-arquitectos-photo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Archdaily</a></figcaption> </figure></div><h3>Fordypningsrommet Fleinvær by TYIN Tegnestue Architects and Rental Eggertsson Architects</h3><p>坐落在挪威 Fleinvr 群岛岩石景观中的这九座小屋，意在让客人们把忙碌的日程安排转换成“安静、灵感和与自然真实的接触”，被看作是世界上最北部的艺术家驻地。</p><p>九座度假小屋都是以舒适的室内环境为特色，用木质家具和蓬松的毛皮作为装饰品。设计从陆地上伸出，它们的外部覆盖着可持续的硬木，九个小屋中的每一个都设计有不同的用途，按功能分隔，有睡眠区、厨房、工作室、灵感室、澡堂甚至桑拿房。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071010SzsTtnEHXjlLAwP3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.548900\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901120710111zrgpXKGqTCtDOQL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.739609\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071010G6ogTIfcr4i8UdnZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071012l0JXDV37HFWbeonk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071012ngeD1MowqZ4dJ2vV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071012GPivbKqtyQgBMN74.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.614914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071013VO8JdbxXtNL7Isvh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071013xeF9A3CoUEcDhwQK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500664\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Villa Baronessina by Walter Angonese and Manfred Alois Mayr</h3><p>Villa Baronessa 别墅是一座贵族宫殿的前花园别墅，意大利白云石山脉的山峰构成了这座酒店的背景，靠近 Kaltern am See 葡萄酒村的历史中心。</p><p>设计师 Walter Angonese 和艺术家 Manfred Alois Mayr 对其进行了翻新扩建，既保留了建筑的原始风格，又添入了不一样的色彩气氛和居住体验。</p><p>除了起居，用餐和烹饪区外，这所房子还设有四间卧室，楼上另一间客厅（配有一张沙发床）、一间桑拿浴室和一个酒窖。露台可直接通往阳光甲板，设有无边泳池，享有周围葡萄园的自然景致。客人可以在户外享受遮阳篷，附近设有带日光浴床的宽敞地中海花园。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071051GBD4A1aJZb3Ux0Hd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.572825\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071051gHNhlxvSzMGRY89c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071052k2hoSncNpOyLViQw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901120710522M6zoPv1QedSOAVU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071052Tc1FkJMh29Iy0Aip.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071053NviADPrFc1aMeTKo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Black H by Dualchas Architects</h3><p>这家位于苏格兰 Skye 岛上的紧凑型度假小屋，每次只能接待两位客人。其生活空间两侧是大开口，旨在让客人沉浸在戏剧性的狂风暴雨景观中。</p><p>为了优化两个方向的景观，房子位于山顶，并在两端采用落地玻璃，使得视觉体验最优化。建筑物前部和后部的两个露台提供了捕捉日出和日落的地点，同时俯瞰着 Harlosh 周围地区的草原、海湾和入口。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901120711494YrOnxsou0ktl3b9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.623096\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071151tRTKVosq9i75Ieyp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071151zIE34rJhW1mpFVXM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.697547\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071154LkvrCg1SWZ5sOD9M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.502961\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071259PN8MYIsktjDczHvi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190112071259ckXjCJNd4l5vqTS3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/12/24/harlosh-dualchas-architects-minimalist-holiday-home-scotland-isle-skye-architecture/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption> </figure></div>"}